Class FacebookVideoDescription

  • java.lang.Object
    • service.tut.pori.facebookjazz.FacebookVideoDescription

  • public class FacebookVideoDescription
extends java.lang.Object
    Video description retrieved from Facebook.

    Optional Elements

    • commentList
    • likeCount
    • location

    XML Example

    <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<videoDescription>
  <likeCount>4075233559748723039</likeCount>
  <createdTimestamp>1970-04-09T03:49:13+0200</createdTimestamp>
  <commentList>
    <createdTimestamp>1996-12-29T23:31:54+0200</createdTimestamp>
    <from>fCIllhUskRevETJgFAagrWzgReJpqbnmOXTWJboVWpmveJftsnbUnUtopfcSfPfm</from>
    <likeCount>5305540543807804504</likeCount>
    <message>anpsLuqUerbIoJTfuFHecjEYIVzgmkNCRFtxJHlRdZffeZmtJPuFlEmqeDAJleIP</message>
  </commentList>
  <from>iyTCkvtjqeZKrlzZevdFgsZyutccPUdCNsjdDYDJOzvSVMZVuTCvWcaMZRcxcFCf</from>
  <updatedTimestamp>1971-07-30T11:57:14+0200</updatedTimestamp>
  <description>RMlOHJkXHuRxqHTwLxhQPpxHQirsVhgSlLnXzWMTZLSUqCoqTAccsBWNrJYUOpzp</description>
</videoDescription>
